For first time you have to run
git submodule update --init # get latest version of tiger hash from github.com

To install do:
make
make tiger # Lunux
make tiger-win # Windows

To start hub do
./EADC # Linux
EADC.bat # Windows

And check it on adc://localhost:4111

Also try run "!help" in chat.

First registered user (by !regme pass) will be superuser.


Requirements:
* make
* gcc (MinGW)
* erlang-otp

Troubleshooting:

If you got "error: erl_driver.h: No such file or directory" when run 'make tiger' than please read deps/tiger/README
